==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Terminator
<hw>Ter"mi*na`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., he who
limits or sets bounds.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which,
terminates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>The dividing line between the
illuminated and the unilluminated part of the moon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- The Terminator. Arnold Schwarzenegger. -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Terminatory</ent>⟦br⟧
